{"tid":148871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<一地兩檢>《基本法》第18條保障內地法律不能在香港特區實施","createTime":"2017-03-09T00:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T04:41:14.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b3a23a90aa79e28f632f02bc5c4eae3b93a083c","tid":148871,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T00:19:12.000Z","msg":"「一地兩檢」：提醒懶惰議員<br />\n「一地兩檢」的關鍵問題是，《基本法》第18條保障內地法律不能在香港特區實施。在香港進行「一地兩檢」，必然涉及在香港境內執行內地法律，所以與第18條有衝突。香港特區固然無權立法容許內地人員來港執法，但同樣亦不能自行執行內地法律，因為問題不在「誰執法」，而是在「執甚麼法」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/一地兩檢-提醒懶惰議員/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%A9%E6%AA%A2-%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%E6%87%B6%E6%83%B0%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%2F&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=620c0fc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%B0%E5%85%A9%E6%AA%A2-%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%E6%87%B6%E6%83%B0%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%2F&h=71fc467d\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/一地兩檢-提醒懶惰議員/</a>"},{"pid":"2e61c4f8c0a1dd916a970b0f57c247a5e1a59699","tid":148871,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T00:24:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72da427c33878567d3c2631fa80fc9882877849","tid":148871,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T00:26:40.000Z","msg":"共匪：I'm the law <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最多釋法滿足你班『守法』港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3eeee177340f7bbace2016863dbb13c64fc378","tid":148871,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T00:27:00.000Z","msg":"中共出聲<br />\n保皇倡議人大釋法<br />\n飯民做SHOW<br />\n成功釋法<br />\n飯民高呼民主最黑暗一日"},{"pid":"97825db6fc41618de8561cc140c8a1921f5a68d6","tid":148871,"uid":44358,"like":0,"d